  ## 🔍 Insights
  
  ## 📌 ZombieAgent: New ChatGPT Vulnerabilities Let Data Theft Continue and Spread
  
  Radware’s [Zvika Babo](https://www.linkedin.com/article/edit/7421868819025059841/#) breaks down “ZombieAgent” abuse paths where prompt injection + agent memory / tool access / connectors enable persistent data exposure, lateral spread across sessions, and follow-on abuse through connected apps and agent workflows. [https://www.radware.com/blog/threat-intelligence/zombieagent/](https://www.radware.com/blog/threat-intelligence/zombieagent/)
  
