  ## 📌 BodySnatcher: Broken Authentication and Agentic Hijacking in ServiceNow
  
  [AppOmni](https://www.linkedin.com/article/edit/7421868819025059841/#)’s [Aaron C.](https://www.linkedin.com/article/edit/7421868819025059841/#) details how a ServiceNow Virtual Agent API + Now Assist AI Agents flaw enabled unauthenticated impersonation using only an email address, bypassing MFA/SSO assumptions and allowing hijacked agent workflows to access data and actions as the victim. [https://appomni.com/ao-labs/bodysnatcher-agentic-ai-security-vulnerability-in-servicenow](https://appomni.com/ao-labs/bodysnatcher-agentic-ai-security-vulnerability-in-servicenow/)
  
