  ## Overview of the Best Cybersecurity Newsletters
  
  ### 1\. [SANS](https://www.sans.org/newsletters/) — For cybersecurity training
  
  [![SANS, a cybersecurity newsletters](https://thectoclub.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/13/2024/08/sans-cybersecurity-newsletter.png)](https://www.sans.org/newsletters/) _SANS Cybersecurity newsletters (_ [_Source_](https://www.sans.org/newsletters/) _)_
  
  The SANS newsletter provides cybersecurity experts with timely updates on threats, vulnerabilities, and trends from the trusted SANS Institute.
  
  - **Audience:** Cybersecurity professionals, IT managers, and anyone interested in cybersecurity training and updates
  - **Newsletter Frequency:** Weekly and monthly
  - **Cost:** Free
  - [Subscribe Here](https://www.sans.org/newsletters/)
  
  **Why Subscribe:**
  
  SANS provides valuable insights through its three cybersecurity newsletters, NewsBites, @RISK, and OUCH!, covering cybersecurity news updates, cyber attacks, vulnerabilities, and security awareness tips. The SANS newsletter is available in over 25 languages and covers various countries and territories.
  
